%% request-flow — thin CLI to daemon to loop, and the event stream back.
%% SoT for site/public/diagrams/request-flow.svg (npm run render-diagrams).
%% Grounded in site/src/app/docs/overview/how-it-runs/page.tsx
%% (core/server/ipc_server/poller.py, core/agent/loop/agent_loop.py).
flowchart TD
  CLI["geode thin CLI (REPL)"] -->|free text| SOCK["~/.geode/cli.sock<br/>Unix socket, line-delimited JSON"]
  SOCK --> POLLER["serve daemon: CLIPoller<br/>core/server/ipc_server/poller.py"]
  POLLER -->|lanes: session, global| LOOP["AgenticLoop<br/>core/agent/loop/agent_loop.py<br/>while stop_reason == tool_use"]
  LOOP --> CAP["tools (ToolRegistry) / MCP servers / skills"]
  CAP --> LOOP
  LOOP -->|events stream back| SOCK
  SOCK -->|rendered events| CLI
